{"tid":1576070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［核彈]原來港鐵未卜先知淘大會有衝突 老早已經叫員工唔好返總部做嘢","createTime":"2019-09-17T05:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T10:09:27.000Z","uid":28114,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"94ad8aacaa3dd510bb5ca82fe5fc73e8d34c9d63","tid":1576070,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:33:51.000Z","msg":"（核彈！港鐵未卜先知淘大會有衝突！）有位係港鐵總部返工的朋友向狠人報料，港鐵在9月12日(上星期四)send咗封email比佢地部門嘅員工，叫佢地9月14-15日唔好返總部做嘢！（朋友話中秋節叫人早啲番屋企就好正常嘅，但叫員工唔好番大樓做嘢，就好奇怪，佢話除咗8月26日有人嚟示威叫人唔好番HQ之外，係未試過叫人唔好番HQ！）<br />\n<br />\n到左9月14日，就發生一批「愛國人士」大鬧淘大事件，仲攪到出晒防暴入商場亂捉亂打街坊！<br />\n<br />\n再次證明黨鐵、黑警、黑社會互相合作！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9anD0y8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9anD0y8.jpg&h=467266f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/130944961581628?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110776013598523%2Fposts%2F130944961581628%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=3b019388\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/130944961581628?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"0e37647e300e7a0ddef5afb7f58a3234e88c57a9","tid":1576070,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"d74aef93d016b051cb1777038c56c6d2cb27a328","tid":1576070,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedB